        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> The ability to cast force or tech powers</em><br />You've practiced making your powers more difficult to avoid, learning techniques that grant you the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>When a creature rolls a 1 on the d20 roll of a saving throw against a power you cast that deals damage, they instead take the highest number possible for the damage die.</li>\n<li>You learn one at-will power that requires a saving throw. Your casting ability for this at-will power depends on the power list you chose from: Wisdom or Charisma (depending on power alignment) for force powers or Intelligence for tech powers.</li>\n</ul>",
